{"tid":1526843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《黨鐵跳閘》唔敢跳閘既乖乖女同我入黎睇！唔洗推唔洗跳既方法","createTime":"2019-09-01T07:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T10:07:02.000Z","uid":233614,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"94915842092c867064200079802ea0e1e8f8676f","tid":1526843,"uid":233614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:46:27.000Z","msg":"平時我都做開乖乖女 所以我好明大家淆底既感受<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 對付紅色門閘機</span></span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">可以抽走銀包張8達通 <span style=\"color: gold;\">貼住前面入閘既人扮拍卡過閘</span></span><br />\n岩岩第一次試 個閘周圍仲要有4個職員好近望住 我貼住佢行果時個閘仲要響左 只要拎住個銀包目無表情咁自信快步行過就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 對付碌碌閘機</span> </span><br />\n <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.1 最好搵殘疾人士閘機！然後用同1. 一樣既方法過</span> </span><br />\n 2.2 夠瘦既可以係側邊空隙過 <br />\n 2.3冇人同你一齊過殘疾人士或者唔夠瘦先跳！禁住兩邊閘機會易好多<br />\n 2.4 其他post睇話大力推支棍都得 但朋友話大力撞會好痛要好大力同仲要岩位 即係要練 冇試過唔推薦 希望試過既弱質女流可以開心share<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\">如果真係不幸被發現 有職員黎緊你就快步行/跑走 佢打份工又年紀大唔會追你好遠</span><br />\n<br />\n雖然我上到月台之後嚇到手都震埋 但突登到一次心理關口後就OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97bae41649444dc4e38bfda9f7c1baba769cffba","tid":1526843,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:47:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72cf98cfb91e86d491da542a4c82c56bb57cac85","tid":1526843,"uid":60398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:56:58.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n[制裁黨鐵] 低調跳閘方法 必定通關<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1524993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1524993</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"